			 Dhammapada - 395
%
I do not call him a holy man because of his
lineage or high-born mother. If he is full of
impeding attachments, he is just a supercilious
man. But who is free from impediments and
clinging—him do I call a holy man.

			 Dhammapada - 396
%
He who, having cut off all fetters, trembles no
